import {Form,Main,Input,Button,Col,Label,TextArea,InputLabel, Head} from './style'
const DiscussForm=()=>{
    return( <><Head color="#fff">GET A FREE QUOTE.</Head>
         <Main>
           
           <Form>
             <Col><InputLabel >     <Label for="html">Full Name (required)</Label><Input/></InputLabel>
             <InputLabel >     <Label for="html">Company</Label><Input/></InputLabel>
  </Col><Col><InputLabel >     <Label for="html">Email (required)
</Label><Input/></InputLabel>
  <InputLabel >     <Label for="html">Phone
</Label><Input/></InputLabel></Col>
        <InputLabel > <Label for="html">Project Details (required)</Label><TextArea/></InputLabel>
        </Form>
        <Button>GET A QUATE</Button></Main>
        </>
        )
}
export default DiscussForm;
